						"title": "Try Cloudflare Zero Trust",
						"subtitle": " Modernize your network and protect your workforce with our unified cloud-native platform",
						"copy": "![Hero  blade - Zero-trust integrations](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/2Oomvz9nxbYQ6wGDcwQwFl/c451752ef1193f42716653c3629a394b/Enterprise.svg)\n\nExperience how Cloudflare simplifies Zero Trust, including our identity and endpoint integrations.\n\nToday's distributed work environment calls for a distributed approach to security. The \"perimeter\" no longer exists, and traditional remote access solutions like VPNs can't meet modern security or performance expectations. \n\nZTNA provides simple, secure access between any user and app, on any device, in any location by verifying every request based on identity, device posture, and other context—without the need for backhauling or on-prem appliances. This modern approach eliminates the \"balancing act\" between security and user experience, enabling your business by enhancing both.\n",
